#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta title=\"Tails report for April, 2014\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"گزارش آوریل ۲۰۱۴ تیلز\"]]\n"

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Releases\n"
msgstr "انتشارها\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Tails 1.0 was released on April 29."
msgstr "تیلز ۱٫۰ روز ۲۹ آوریل منتشر شد."

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Metrics\n"
msgstr "متریک‌ها\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Tails has been started more than 292 595 times in April.  This make 9 753 "
"boots a day in average."
msgstr ""
"تیلز بیش از ۲۹۲٫۵۹۵ بار در ماه آوریل راه‌اندازی شد. یعنی به طور متوسط ۹٫۷۵۳ "
"راه‌اندازی در روز."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "35 029 downloads of the OpenPGP signature of Tails ISO."
msgstr "۳۵٫۰۲۹ دانلود امضای اُپن‌پی‌جی‌پی ایزوی تیلز."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "105 reports were received through WhisperBack."
msgstr "۱۰۵ گزارش از طریق ویسپربک دریافت شدند."

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Code\n"
msgstr "کد\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"* Quite some work was put into adapting Tails to Debian 7 (Wheezy).\n"
"  The result will be released on June 10, as Tails 1.1.\n"
"  - Thanks to the amazing work done in Debian by Ulrike, we are\n"
msgstr ""
"* کارهای بسیاری برای تطبیق تیلز با دبیان ۷ (Wheezy) انجام شد\n"
"  نتیجه روز ۱۰ ژوئن در قالب تیلز ۱٫۱ منتشر خواهد شد.\n"
" - به لطف کار عالی Ulrike در دبیان،\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    feature/6608-OpenPGP-signature-verification-in-Nautilus\n"
"    desc=\"almost there\"]] when it comes to adding back support for\n"
"    OpenPGP signature verification in Nautilus ([[!tails_ticket\n"
"    6608]]).\n"
"  - The Vagrant setup was [[!tails_gitweb_branch\n"
"    bugfix/vagrant-ram-bump-for-wheezy desc=\"fixed\"]] to allow\n"
"    building Tails/Wheezy images in RAM ([[!tails_ticket 7132]]).\n"
"  - Synaptic was made to [[!tails_gitweb_branch\n"
"    bugfix/7055-drop-default-APT-release desc=\"start again\"]] on\n"
"    Wheezy ([[!tails_ticket 7055]]).\n"
"  - The Debian Mozilla team's repository used on the devel branch\n"
"    [[!tails_gitweb_branch bugfix/use-Wheezy-repo-for-debian-mozilla\n"
"    desc=\"was updated\"]] for Wheezy ([[!tails_ticket 7063]]).\n"
"  - The latest version of the MAT [[!tails_gitweb_branch\n"
"    feature/mat-0.5.2 desc=\"is now installed\"]] ([[!tails_ticket\n"
"    5792]]).\n"
"  - Initial progress [[!tails_gitweb_branch\n"
"    feature/6342-update-camouflage-for-gnome3 desc=\"was made\"]] to\n"
"    update the Windows camouflage.\n"
msgstr ""
"    feature/6608-OpenPGP-signature-verification-in-Nautilus\n"
"    desc=\"تقریباً در پایان\"]] کارمان برای اضافه کردن پشتیبانی اضافه\n"
"برای تأیید امضاهای اُپن‌پی‌جی‌پی در ناتیلوس هستیم ([[!tails_ticket\n"
"    6608]]).\n"
"  - تنظیم واگرانت برای اجازهٔ ساخت تصاویر Tails/Wheezy در حافظهٔ تصادفی\n"
"    [[!tails_gitweb_branch\n"
"   bugfix/vagrant-ram-bump-for-wheezy desc=\"ترمیم شد\"]]([[!tails_ticket "
"7132]]).\n"
"  - سیناپتیک طوری تنظیم شد که در Wheezy\n"
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch\n"
"    bugfix/7055-drop-default-APT-release desc=\"دوباره راه‌اندازی شود\"]] ([["
"!tails_ticket 7055]]).\n"
"  - مخزن تیم موزیلای دبیان که برای شاخهٔ devel به کار می‌رفت برای Wheezy\n"
"    [[!tails_gitweb_branch bugfix/use-Wheezy-repo-for-debian-mozilla\n"
"    desc=\"ارتقاء داده شد\"]] ([[!tails_ticket 7063]]).\n"
"  - آخرین نسخهٔ MAT [[!tails_gitweb_branch\n"
"    feature/mat-0.5.2 desc=\"نصب شده‌است\"]] ([[!tails_ticket\n"
"    5792]]).\n"
"  - پیشرفت‌هایی مقدماتی برای ارتقای استتار ویندوزی [[!tails_gitweb_branch\n"
"    feature/6342-update-camouflage-for-gnome3 desc=\"حاصل شد\"]].\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "    [[!tails_ticket 6342]]\n"
msgstr "    [[!tails_ticket 6342]]\n"

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid "The APT suite being used when building from the stable branch"
msgstr "بستهٔ اپت مورد استفاده هنگام ساخت از شاخهٔ پایدار"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  bugfix/7022-use-stable-APT-suite-when-building-from-stable-branch\n"
"  desc=\"was corrected\"]] ([[!tails_ticket 7022]]).\n"
"* The new logo [[!tails_gitweb_branch\n"
"  feature/7096-integrate-the-new-logo-in-about-tails desc=\"was\n"
"  integrated\"]] in the *About Tails* dialog ([[!tails_ticket 7096]]).\n"
"* Some Vagrant compatibility issues [[!tails_gitweb_branch\n"
"  bugfix/fix-vagrant-compatibility-issues desc=\"were fixed\"]]\n"
"  ([[!tails_ticket 7134]]).\n"
"* The blacklisting of directory authority keys that have been used\n"
"  with versions of OpenSSL affected by Heartbleed\n"
"  [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/tor-0.2.4.21-1+tails1_d70.wheezy+1\n"
"  desc=\"was backported\"]] into our Tor packages.\n"
"* Our modified Tor Launcher [[!tails_gitweb_branch\n"
"  feature/tor-launcher-0.2.5.3 desc=\"was updated\"]] to avoid\n"
"  [[!tails_ticket 6934 desc=\"pretending that we ship a default set of "
"bridges\"]].\n"
"* I2P [[!tails_gitweb_branch bugfix/i2p_incoming desc=\"was explicitly\n"
"  told\"]] that it cannot receive inbound connections ([[!tails_ticket "
"7070]]).\n"
"* An attempt at migrating our source tree to live-build 3.x\n"
msgstr ""
"  bugfix/7022-use-stable-APT-suite-when-building-from-stable-branch\n"
"  desc=\"تصحیح شد\"]] ([[!tails_ticket 7022]]).\n"
"* لوگوی جدید در قسمت *دربارهٔ تیلز*\n"
" [[!tails_gitweb_branch\n"
"  feature/7096-integrate-the-new-logo-in-about-tails desc=\"به‌روز شد\"]] ([["
"!tails_ticket 7096]]).\n"
"* برخی مشکلات سازگاری واگرانت [[!tails_gitweb_branch\n"
"  bugfix/fix-vagrant-compatibility-issues desc=\"رفع شدند\"]]\n"
"  ([[!tails_ticket 7134]]).\n"
"* ایجاد فهرست سیاه کلیدهای مدیریتی پوشه‌ها \n"
"  که در نسخه‌های اُپن‌اس‌اس‌ال تحت تأثیر هارت‌بلید به کار رفته بودندبه بسته‌"
"های تور ما\n"
"  [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/tor-0.2.4.21-1+tails1_d70.wheezy+1\n"
"  desc=\"بک‌پورت شد\"]].\n"
"* راه‌انداز تور تغییریافتهٔ ما برای اجتناب از [[!tails_ticket 6934 desc=\""
"وانمود کردن به گنجاندن مجموعه‌ای\n"
"  پیش‌فرض از پل‌ها\"]] [[!tails_gitweb_branch\n"
"  feature/tor-launcher-0.2.5.3 desc=\"ارتقاء داده شد\"]].\n"
"* به طور شفاف به I2P [[!tails_gitweb_branch bugfix/i2p_incoming desc=\"\n"
"  گفته شد\"]] که نمی‌تواند اتصالات درون‌سو را دریافت کند([[!tails_ticket "
"7070]]).\n"
"* تلاشی برای انتقال شاخهٔ کد خود به live-build 3.x\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "  [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/live-build-3.x desc=\"was made\"]]\n"
msgstr "  [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/live-build-3.x desc=\"انجام شد\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  ([[!tails_ticket 5691]]). It is still entirely unclear whether the\n"
"  cost/benefit ratio is worth it, especially because live-build 4.x\n"
"  has already gone quite further in terms of incompatibilities, and is\n"
"  far from being ready for prime-time yet.\n"
"* A patch to make the Greeter's help window resolution-aware was\n"
"  "
"[proposed](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-dev/2014-April/005451.html)\n"
"  ([[!tails_ticket 7009]]).\n"
"* Another proposed patch aims at fixing the Tails Installer fonts size\n"
"  on Wheezy ([[!tails_ticket 5673]]).\n"
msgstr ""
"  ([[!tails_ticket 5691]]). هنوز کاملاً نامشخص است که\n"
"  نسبت هزینه/فایدهٔ آن خوب است یا نه، به خصوص که live-build 4.x\n"
"  همین حالا از نظر ناسازگاری‌ها فراتر رفته و \n"
"  هنوز تا آماده شدن برای استفادهٔ واقعی کار زیادی دارد.\n"
"* بسته‌ای برای حساس کردن پنجرهٔ کمک خوشامدگو نسبت به وضوح تصویر\n"
"  [پیشنهاد شد](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-"
"dev/2014-April/005451.html)\n"
"  ([[!tails_ticket 7009]]).\n"
"* بسته‌ٔ دیگری با هدف درست کردن اندازهٔ قلم‌های نصب‌کنندهٔ تیلز\n"
"  در Wheezy ([[!tails_ticket 5673]]) پیشنهاد شده‌است.\n"

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Documentation and website\n"
msgstr "مستندسازی و تارنما\n"

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid "The [[support/FAQ]] was published."
msgstr "[[support/FAQ]] منتشر شد."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"The [[logo|promote/logo]] that [[won|news/and_the_winner_is]] the contest "
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/logo desc=\"was integrated\"]] in the "
"website, and on the boot loader's splash screen ([[!tails_ticket 7090]])."
msgstr ""
"[[لوگویی|promote/logo]] که [[برندهٔ|news/and_the_winner_is]] مسابقه شد، در "
"تارنما و نیز در صفحهٔ اسپلش بارگذارندهٔ راه‌اندازی [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"feature/logo desc=\"به کار رفت\"]] ([[!tails_ticket 7090]])."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"Some initial steps [were "
"walked](https://git-tails.immerda.ch/451f/tails/log/?h=websitemodernization)  "
"to modernize our website's markup and CSS, including moving to HTML5 and "
"better responsiveness ([[!tails_ticket 7021]]).  Compatibility with older "
"browsers is left to be tested before we can apply these changes to the live "
"website."
msgstr ""
"قدم‌هایی ابتدایی برای مدرن کردن نشانه‌گذاری تارنما و سی‌اس‌اس و نیز استفاده "
"از اچ‌تی‌ام‌ال۵ و نیز حساسیت بیشتر [برداشته شد](https://git-"
"tails.immerda.ch/451f/tails/log/?h=websitemodernization) ([[!tails_ticket "
"7021]]). سازگاری با مرورگرهای قدیمی‌تر همچنان باید پیش از به کار بردن این "
"تغییرات در تارنمای زنده امتحان شود."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"Many documentation pages were deeply reworked as part of [[!tails_ticket "
"5977]]: [[!tails_gitweb_branch doc/why_tor]], [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"doc/vidalia]], [[!tails_gitweb_branch doc/unsafe_browser]], "
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch doc/network-manager]], and [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"doc/introduction]]."
msgstr ""
"بسیاری از صفحات مستندات در بخشی از [[!tails_ticket 5977]] تغییر یافتند: [["
"!tails_gitweb_branch doc/why_tor]]، [[!tails_gitweb_branch doc/vidalia]], [["
"!tails_gitweb_branch doc/unsafe_browser]]، [[!tails_gitweb_branch doc"
"/network-manager]]، و [[!tails_gitweb_branch doc/introduction]]."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"The [[homepage|index]] now [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"doc/mention-Debian-on-the-homepage desc=\"makes it clear\"]] that Tails is "
"based on Debian, Tor, and is Free software."
msgstr ""
"حالا [[صفحهٔ خانه|index]] [[!tails_gitweb_branch doc/mention-Debian-on-the-"
"homepage desc=\"مشخص می‌کند\"]] که تیلز مبتنی بر دبیان و تور بوده و یک نرم‌"
"افزار آزاد است."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"The MAC spoofing documentation [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"doc/7054-explain-why-not-randomising-oui-part-of-mac desc=\"now explains\"]] "
"why we do not randomize the OUI part of MAC addresses."
msgstr ""
"سند جا زدن آدرس مک [[!tails_gitweb_branch doc/7054-explain-why-not-"
"randomising-oui-part-of-mac desc=\"حالا توضیح می‌دهد\"]] که چرا قسمت OUI "
"آدرس‌های مک را تصادفی‌سازی نمی‌کنیم."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"The way to update our Tor Launcher is [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"doc/bridge-mode-design desc=\"now documented\"]]."
msgstr ""
"روش ارتقای راه‌انداز تور ما [[!tails_gitweb_branch doc/bridge-mode-design "
"desc=\"حالا مستند شده‌است\"]]."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"The I2P documentation [[!tails_gitweb_branch_kytv bugfix/I2P-page desc=\"was "
"slightly improved\"]]."
msgstr ""
"سند I2P [[!tails_gitweb_branch_kytv bugfix/I2P-page desc=\"کمی تغییر پیدا "
"کرد\"]]."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid "The CSS of the boxed titles was improved ([[!tails_ticket 6323]])."
msgstr "سی‌اس‌اس عنوان‌های جعبه‌دار بهبود داده شد.([[!tails_ticket 6323]])."

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Translation\n"
msgstr "ترجمه‌ها\n"

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"The German translation team has been making great progress, and we are not "
"considering dropping this language from our website anymore."
msgstr ""
"تیم ترجمهٔ المانی پیشرفت بسیار خوبی داشته‌اند و دیگر این زبان را از تارنما "
"حذف نخواهیم کرد."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid "The French translation team got a new member."
msgstr "تیم ترجمهٔ فرانسوی عضو جدیدی گرفته‌است."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"The Italian translation team has been reviewing strings in Transifex, and "
"working on their internal workflow and processes.  There is hope that they "
"start translating the website soon."
msgstr ""
"تیم ترجمهٔ ایتالیایی در حال بررسی استرینگ‌های Transifex و کار روی روند کار "
"درونی خود بوده‌اند. این احتمال وجود دارد که به زودی شروع به ترجمهٔ تارنما "
"بکنند."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"A list of glossaries used by translation teams [[!tails_ticket 6968 "
"desc=\"is being compiled\"]]."
msgstr ""
"فهرستی از واژه‌های به کاررفته توسط تیم‌های ترجمه [[!tails_ticket 6968 desc=\""
"در حال آماده شدن است\"]]."

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Infrastructure\n"
msgstr "زیرساخت\n"

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"Quite a lot of progress was made to make our automated test suite support "
"Tails based on Debian Wheezy: [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"test/6559-adapt-test-suite-for-Wheezy]], [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"test/6559-adapt-test-suite-for-Wheezy-by-anonym]] ([[!tails_ticket 6559]])."
msgstr ""
"پیشرفت زیادی برای پشتیبانی بستهٔ آزمایشی خودکار ما از تیلز مبتنی بر Debian "
"Wheezy انجام شد: [[!tails_gitweb_branch test/6559-adapt-test-suite-for-"
"Wheezy]]، [[!tails_gitweb_branch test/6559-adapt-test-suite-for-Wheezy-by-"
"anonym]] ([[!tails_ticket 6559]])."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"An automated test case [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"test/6275-boot-device-write-access-via-udisks desc=\"was written\"]] to "
"check write access to the boot device via udisks [[!tails_ticket 6275]]."
msgstr ""
"یک مورد آزمایش خودکار برای بررسی دسترسی نوشتن به دستگاه راه‌اندازی از طریق "
"udisks [[!tails_gitweb_branch test/6275-boot-device-write-access-via-udisks "
"desc=\"نوشته شد\"]] [[!tails_ticket 6275]]."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"Our Jenkins master configuration was migrated to a [[!tails_gitweb_repo "
"puppet-tails desc=\"published module\"]]."
msgstr ""
"پیکربندی اصلی جنکینز ما به [[!tails_gitweb_repo puppet-tails desc=\"ماژول‌"
"های منتشرشده\"]] منتقل شد."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"We now install debomatic from wheezy-backports, for easier maintenance and a "
"more stable infrastructure."
msgstr ""
"حالا debomatic را از wheezy-backports نصب می‌کنیم که باعث نگهداری ساده‌تر و "
"زیرساخت پایدارتر می‌شود."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"Thanks to Alster's suggestion, the boum.org administrators could [add a few "
"security-oriented HTTP "
"headers](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-dev/2014-April/005392.html)  "
"to our website."
msgstr ""
"به لطف پیشنهاد Alster، مدیران boum.org می‌توانند به تارنمای ما [چند سربرگ "
"اچ‌تی‌تی‌پی در رابطه با امنیت اضافه کنند](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail"
"/tails-dev/2014-April/005392.html)."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"Jurre van Bergen has requested an audit by OpenITP's Peer Review Board "
"([[!tails_ticket 6889]])."
msgstr ""
"Jurre van Bergen برای بررسی از سوی OpenITP's Peer Review Board درخواست داده‌"
"است ([[!tails_ticket 6889]])."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"For ethical reasons, we have renamed our *Broken Window* Redmine category to "
"*Hole in the Roof*."
msgstr ""
"به دلایل اخلاقی قسمت ردماین *پنجره‌های شکسته* (Broken Windows) را به *سوراخ "
"سقف* (Hole in the Roof) تغییر دادیم."

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "On-going discussions\n"
msgstr "بحث‌های دنباله‌دار\n"

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"[Improving our "
"website](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-dev/2014-April/005476.html)  "
"in various ways."
msgstr ""
"[بهبود تارنمای ما](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-"
"dev/2014-April/005476.html) به روش‌های مختلف."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"[Making it easy to backup and restore a persistent "
"volume](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-dev/2014-April/005388.html)  "
"([[!tails_ticket 5301]])."
msgstr ""
"[آسان کردن گرفتن نسخهٔ پشتیبان و بازیابی یک درایو "
"مانا](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-dev/2014-April/005388.html)  "
"([[!tails_ticket 5301]])."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"Jacob Appelbaum expressed interest in [getting a grsec-patched Linux "
"kernel](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-dev/2014-April/005413.html)  "
"into Tails. Of course, this requires doing the same in Debian, which is not "
"a trivial mission."
msgstr ""
"جیکوب اپلبام به [گرفتن یک هستهٔ لینوکس grsec-"
"patched](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-dev/2014-April/005413.html)"
" در تیلز ابراز علاقه کرد. البته این کار مستلزم انجام همین کار در دبیان است "
"که کار ساده‌ای نیست."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"[Installing "
"gimp-ufraw?](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-dev/2014-April/005587.html)"
msgstr ""
"[نصب gimp-ufraw؟](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-"
"dev/2014-April/005587.html)"

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"[Installing "
"tcplay?](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-dev/2014-April/005595.html)"
msgstr ""
"[نصب tcplay؟](https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-"
"dev/2014-April/005595.html)"

